Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,------------------------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.32,0:00:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,In the previous episode,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.44,0:00:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Weslie and Sparky are asking Blazey to be their basketball coach.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.52,0:00:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,To everyone’s surprise, an old goat opened the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.08,0:00:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,His identity was only revealed after
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.16,0:00:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,the three goats fell off the cliff and he saved everyone with his pitching skills.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.80,0:00:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The two goats wanted to persuade him to come out of seclusion, but Blazey turned around and ran away.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.92,0:00:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Blazey senior!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.36,0:00:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Blazey, don’t run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.48,0:00:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I will not be your coach.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.04,0:00:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Blazey, please stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.08,0:00:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I said, I’m not going to be your coach.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.48,0:01:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Blazey senior!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.12,0:01:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Who exactly is that masked man? He’s so good at basketball!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.40,0:01:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoever he is,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.60,0:01:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,if I ever see him again, I’ll catch him first.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.32,0:01:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,How could you just meet a master like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.12,0:01:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he going to fall from the sky right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.32,0:01:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.84,0:01:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.52,0:01:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Blazey senior!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.20,0:01:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.28,0:01:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,They caught up so quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.00,0:01:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m sorry, both of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.80,0:01:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m leaving now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.48,0:01:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Blazey senior!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.16,0:01:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s those two goats again.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.08,0:01:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother, don’t you think that old goat’s voice sounds familiar?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.04,0:02:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,He {\i1}is{\i0} that masked man.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.28,0:02:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Catch them!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.08,0:02:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Blazey senior!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.96,0:02:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you guys want to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.36,0:02:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, we want to invite you guys to discuss basketball.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.28,0:02:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What are they trying to do by trapping us here?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.96,0:02:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,They’re making a move.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.96,0:02:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,First boil the water—
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.68,0:02:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Boil the water?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.08,0:02:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Then add rock sugar.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.88,0:02:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Add rock sugar?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.96,0:02:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Sharpen the knife, quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.24,0:02:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Sharpen the knife?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.32,0:02:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Rats are eating goats!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.28,0:02:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Sparky, calm down. Rats don’t eat goats.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.20,0:02:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Blazey senior, what should we do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.32,0:03:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,He can fall asleep at times like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.64,0:03:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,As expected of a senior!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.64,0:03:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,They’re eating goats!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.00,0:03:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Senior Goat, please try the broccoli I cut myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.00,0:03:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Senior!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.88,0:03:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What exactly do you want to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.88,0:03:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Please become our coach!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.04,0:03:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What’s going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.44,0:03:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,On the day of the Basketball Game signing up, we suffered a crushing defeat to that wolf.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.68,0:03:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,For us, it’s an absolute disgrace.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.52,0:03:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Until we met you, we felt you were even more formidable than that wolf.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.64,0:03:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,If you’re willing to teach us basketball, we’re sure we can beat that wolf!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.16,0:03:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m sorry, I can’t agree to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.12,0:04:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to be their coach?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.80,0:04:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Don’t waste your time, they have no chance of playing basketball well.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.96,0:04:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it’s not that Goat Clan could never play basketball well.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.28,0:04:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, you’re an exception.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.28,0:04:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Those two are definitely not a good match.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.92,0:04:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Their skills are so poor, they are utterly helpless.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.88,0:04:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,How about this, you two have a match with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.72,0:04:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,If you two win, I’ll become your coach.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.12,0:04:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,If they win, you’ll release us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.88,0:04:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.56,0:04:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,There’s no need to compete anymore, we’ve already won.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.32,0:04:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Since you have the ability, why not win again and show me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.48,0:04:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, let’s show Coach our strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.12,0:04:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Weslie, you’re better suited to small forward work.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.04,0:05:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Small forward?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.64,0:05:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Small forward is the key to scoring.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.36,0:05:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Your speed and explosiveness will become your powerful weapons.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.36,0:05:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.52,0:05:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You have some basic basketball skills,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.92,0:05:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,strong with good jumping ability, making you suitable for attacking under the basket.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.56,0:05:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You can do power forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.36,0:05:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Power… forward?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.52,0:05:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Power forward is primarily responsible for rebounding and defense.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.44,0:05:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.84,0:05:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,How did you know our unique characteristics?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.32,0:05:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you seen us play?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.40,0:05:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,No time to explain.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.80,0:05:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a trick here that can help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.56,0:05:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.64,0:05:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,As usual, whoever scores ten makes first wins.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.60,0:06:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You should start at your own pace.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.64,0:06:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Can we win like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.72,0:06:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe in Blazey senior.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.12,0:06:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You still have time—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.40,0:06:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,chatting here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.28,0:06:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Don’t worry, there’re still chances.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.84,0:06:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s only their second make; there’re still chances.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.36,0:07:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Score two more makes and you’ll lose; the coach will be ours.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.24,0:07:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,We must defend this shot to have a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.40,0:07:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Chance?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.52,0:07:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You’re overthinking it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.16,0:07:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Don’t underestimate us!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.64,0:07:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,He’s about to shoot.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.56,0:07:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Don’t even think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.92,0:07:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s a feint.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.76,0:07:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.80,0:07:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.52,0:07:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.60,0:07:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Nine makes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.72,0:07:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What to do? We’re losing!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.60,0:08:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay then.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.84,0:08:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Here he comes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.08,0:08:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You’ll definitely get blown 9-0 by the Team Rats.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.44,0:08:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,However, given the arrogant nature of the Team Rats,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.56,0:08:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,they’ll definitely say that when they’re leading by a large margin—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.40,0:08:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay then.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.36,0:08:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as you score one make, you’ll win.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.88,0:08:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,This is your only chance to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.84,0:08:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Quick, get started!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.80,0:08:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I won’t let you pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.04,0:08:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You can’t get past my tight defense.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.00,0:08:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Weslie!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.88,0:09:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Even so, with our current strength,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.52,0:09:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,it’s not guaranteed that we’ll make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.36,0:09:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I don’t expect you guys to score {\i1}ten{\i0} makes at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.44,0:09:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,But I have a trick that will make you score {\i1}one{\i0} make.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.24,0:09:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,They’re using a pick-and-roll.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.72,0:09:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,A pick-and-roll is when the ball handler dribbles towards the player who is about to set a screen.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.32,0:09:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,At the same time, the player setting the screen moves to the position and then remains stationary,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.40,0:09:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,blocking the opponent’s shoulder impact
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.04,0:09:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,and screening to help the ball handler escape the defender.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.32,0:09:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Get back on defense quickly, Shu Er!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.88,0:09:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think you can score against me just with a pick-and-roll?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.76,0:10:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Don’t forget I’m here to defend!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.92,0:10:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Feint to pass the ball!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.40,0:10:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Weslie, this is the only chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.80,0:10:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.56,0:10:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I won’t let this opportunity go to waste.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.72,0:10:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.64,0:10:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Blazey senior,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.40,0:10:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Please see our determination.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.24,0:10:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s in!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.40,0:10:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my only chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.56,0:11:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys won.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.00,0:11:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I keep my word.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.68,0:11:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You can go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.28,0:11:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,No more freebies next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.52,0:11:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,We don’t need your freebies; our Goat Team will win again next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.76,0:11:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,That’s right, it’s our Goat Team.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.20,0:11:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Our?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.40,0:11:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you’re willing to be our coach?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.56,0:11:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Coach, wait for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.20,0:11:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Coach!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.48,0:11:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Slowy, we’ve found Coach Blazey!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.64,0:11:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Long time no see, Slowy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.24,0:11:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You’re—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.92,0:11:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Slowy, what’s wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.84,0:11:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn’t this the coach you asked us to find?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.20,0:11:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it really you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.36,0:11:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,The little goat over there,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.68,0:12:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,do you want to join the basketball team?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.00,0:12:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Basketball is very interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.24,0:12:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What has happened to you, senior, over the years?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.84,0:12:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to know too!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.08,0:12:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Let’s go train.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.12,0:12:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, Coach.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.88,0:12:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye, Mr. Slowy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.12,0:12:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye.
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,------------------------------------------------------
